<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit und Unterstützung für N. Copelmann, Jude zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_156" id="77v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l9">Augſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l10"> <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> freunde / vns hat fürgelegt Copelman Jude / 
<del rend="strikethrough">hie bey </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">geſeſʒen </del> / wie er etwaſʒ ſach 
<del rend="strikethrough"> bey </del> vor ew cʒu handeln hab / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l12">er ew wol fürgeben wirdet . / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">dem eg </del> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l13">wıllen / dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ vnſerm <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> . 
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr </del> geleit geben / vnd Jm in <expan>de<ex>n</ex>ſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l14">
<add>ſeinen <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> furderlichen vnd beholffen ſein wollet Als wir etc . daʒ <expan>woll<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_156" id="77v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Augspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> freunde, uns hat fürgelegt Copelman, jude,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie er etwasz sach vor ew czu handeln hab, als er ew wol
            fürgeben wirdet. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> unserm
                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> geleit geben und im in
                <expan>de<ex>n</ex>s<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<add>seinen <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> furderlichen und beholffen sein wollet.
            Als wir etc. Daz <expan>woll<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
